overview: The stars are back to count down your votes of the CRAPPIEST ideas wrestling has ever come up with. The experts at WRESTLECRAP gave us a list of their top 20 selections and you voted the list down to a precious, crappy 5!  What were the gimmicks that made us groan, laugh, or downright ashamed to be watching wrestling? Check out pro wrestling’s first countdown show as the season 2 stars rate your selections and share their thoughts…  …on WRESTLING’S MOST…CRAPPY GIMMICK!
title: Wrestling’s Most…Crappy Gimmick
